00:11:21.019 --> 00:11:26.019
The combination of God's love, prayer, and his spirit

00:11:26.019 --> 00:11:34.019
can give you the strength and the wisdom you need to maintain a balanced routine of spiritual activities

00:11:34.019 --> 00:11:40.019
while making sure to care for your family responsibilities.

00:11:40.019 --> 00:11:47.019
In the video, the believing mates took advantage of all the spiritual food that was available

00:11:47.019 --> 00:11:50.019
