00:12:10.019 --> 00:12:15.019
and feel disappointed by your mates' words or actions.

00:12:15.019 --> 00:12:20.019
And yet, regardless of your situation,

00:12:20.019 --> 00:12:26.019
Jehovah can supply you with the power to keep setting a fine example

00:12:26.019 --> 00:12:33.399
as you keep on praying that your mate will eventually respond to the truth.

